The paper deals with age estimation from face images, which is a common task in computer vision. The proposed method involves the use of deep learning models such as ResNets and RoR, which are commonly used in computer vision tasks such as image classification and object detection. The use of LSTM units and attention mechanisms also suggests a focus on sequential data processing, which is a common theme in natural language processing and time series analysis. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category for this paper is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.MM (Multimedia), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
